Package: herdr
Title: herdr
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Juan Carlos", "Baez", email = "juancarlos.baez@bc3research.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
		   comment = c(ORCID ="0000-0002-7067-265X")))
Description: Description: Provides a comprehensive set of tools for calculating livestock 
    greenhouse gas emissions based on Spanish national standards. The package 
    includes functions to process animal census data for cattle, sheep, and 
    goats, integrating specific emission factors and rate parameters. It 
    facilitates the estimation of direct and indirect emissions, such as 
    methane and nitrous oxide, following standardized methodologies for 
    environmental reporting.
URL: https://github.com/JuanCBM99/herdr
